%% Data Pipeline Flow
flowchart TD

RAW[Raw OHLCV per symbol/TF] --> RS[Resample/Aggregate per TF]
RS --> IND[Compute Indicators per TF]
IND --> ALN[Align to Base TF Index\n(reindex + ffill)]
ALN --> FTR[Concatenate Features\n(1h + 4h + ...)]
FTR --> SPLIT[Time Split\n(train / val / test)]
SPLIT --> FIT[Fit Scalers on Train]
FIT --> TRN[Transform Train]
SPLIT --> EVAL[Transform Val/Test]
TRN --> ENV[XTradeEnvironment]
EVAL --> ENV
